From: Olaf Stenvers <olaf.stenvers@kvw.nl>

re: susceptibility of apes to human pathogens
---------------------------------------------
The readers of ProMED-mail might be interested to know that a synopsis on
the matter of transmission of human pathogens to mountain gorilla's (Ape
Tourism and Human Diseases: How close should we get?) can be found at
<http://www.mountaingorillas.org/files/ourwork/Homsy_rev.pdf>.
The publication includes an overview of documented evidence of
susceptibility of apes to human pathogens.
--
OFJ Stenvers, DVM, PhD
Coordinating Centre for Zoonoses
Food and Consumer Product Safety Authority
Directorate of Inspection
PO Box 19506
2500 CM The Hague
Netherlands
<olaf.stenvers@vwa.nl>
